<h2>Italian Soda</h2>

<div>
	<h3>Ingredients</h3>
	
	<ul>
	  <li>Ice</li>
	  <li>Fruit syrup</li>
	  <li>Milk</li>
	  <li>Vodka (optional)</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<div>
	<h3>Method</h3>
	
	<ul>
		<li>Add ice to whisky glass</li>
		<li>Add 25ml syrup (or to taste)</li>
  </ul>
</div>

Link to this recipe: http://jsrn.net/tablecloth/#cocktails/italiansoda